Document: AnimationNodeTransition
Path: godot/classes/class_animationnodetransition.rst
Summary: Describes the properties of the AnimationNodeTransition class, which controls transitions between animations.

Properties
* allow_transition_to_self (bool): If true, the transition node can transition to the currently playing animation. Default: false.
* input_count (int): The number of inputs to the transition node. Default: 0.
* xfade_curve (Curve): The curve used to control the crossfade between animations.
* xfade_time (float): The duration of the crossfade between animations in seconds. Default: 0.0.
